code: @Override public Set<AnnotatedMethod<? super X>> getMethods() {     Set<AnnotatedMethod<? super X>> methods = new HashSet<>(decoratedType.getMethods()).     for (AnnotatedMethod<? super X> method : decoratedMethods) {         methods.remove(method).         methods.add(method).     }     return Collections.unmodifiableSet(methods). }
@Override public Set<AnnotatedField<? super X>> getFields() {     return decoratedType.getFields(). }
